messages.messageBody:
Oh, it wasn't me. Someone else used it first! (the line I mean). But we
found out it was Star Hustler, now re-named to Stargazer :-) Still
airing!

Where is O.C.?

ShannonCC

J Salicos wrote:
> Hi Shannon, I don't remember the name of the show,but
> I do know that your letter sparked a memory of that
> line. I always looked up especially when I was growing
> up. I would dream of flying to the moon. I could see
> it at night from my window. If you're ever in O.C. let
> me know and we'll have a moon party!
> Jill
